#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.special.multigammaln.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.special.multigammaln"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:1 of
msgid ""
"Returns the log of multivariate gamma, also sometimes called the "
"generalized gamma."
msgstr "返回多元 gamma 函数的对数，有时也称为广义 gamma 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:4 of
msgid "The multivariate gamma is computed for each item of `a`."
msgstr "为 `a` 的每个元素计算多元 gamma 函数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:6 of
msgid "The dimension of the space of integration."
msgstr "积分空间的维度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:9 of
msgid ""
"**res** -- The values of the log multivariate gamma at the given points "
"`a`."
msgstr "**res** -- 在给定点 `a` 处的对数多元 gamma 函数值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:13 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:14 of
msgid ""
"The formal definition of the multivariate gamma of dimension d for a real"
" `a` is"
msgstr "对于实数 `a`，维度为 d 的多元 gamma 函数的形式定义为"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:17 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\Gamma_d(a) = \\int_{A>0} e^{-tr(A)} |A|^{a - (d+1)/2} dA"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:21 of
msgid ""
"with the condition :math:`a > (d-1)/2`, and :math:`A > 0` being the set "
"of all the positive definite matrices of dimension `d`.  Note that `a` is"
" a scalar: the integrand only is multivariate, the argument is not (the "
"function is defined over a subset of the real set)."
msgstr ""
"条件为 :math:`a > (d-1)/2`，且 :math:`A > 0` 是所有维度为 `d` 的正定矩阵"
"组成的集合。注意 `a` 是一个标量：被积函数是多元的，但参数不是（该函数定义"
"在实数集的一个子集上）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:26 of
msgid "This can be proven to be equal to the much friendlier equation"
msgstr "可以证明它等于更友好的等式"

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:28 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid "\\Gamma_d(a) = \\pi^{d(d-1)/4} \\prod_{i=1}^{d} \\Gamma(a - (i-1)/2)."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:33 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.special.gamma_funcs.multigammaln:34 of
msgid ""
"R. J. Muirhead, Aspects of multivariate statistical theory (Wiley Series "
"in probability and mathematical statistics)."
msgstr ""

